title: The Replacements / The Shit Hits the Fans
description:
The Replacements / The Shit Hits the Fans
 
Live album by The Replacements 
Released January 25, 1985 
Recorded November 11, 1984 
Label Twin/Tone 
 
The Shit Hits the Fans is a Twin/Tone Records (TTR 8443) cassette-only live album by The Replacements which was released January 25, 1985. It was recorded live at The Bowery, Oklahoma City, Oklahoma on November 11th, 1984. Cassette J-Card Cover Art by Chris Mars. According to the Twin/Tone website, 10,000 copies were produced, of which 9,276 sold immediately. The rest were given away as promotional copies.
